rComments: Doesn't give answers to assigned homework questions. Lectures are taken directly from the textbook.

His lectures are extremely boring and dry and he doesn't explain concepts clearly. His midterms were not very difficult however his final was extremely difficult and he asked us questions that we had never seen before that were very unclear. Overall, I would not take a class with this prof as I taught myself most of the material from the textbook.
Wasn't really that bad of a teacher, he just didn't knew how to explain or answer a question properly. Really funny guy tho, and I liked how sympathic he was when you go talk to him !!!!

This teacher did not once use the textbook. Nor did he explain  the concepts using examples. He read word for word the powerpoint and didnt appreciate when students asked questions. The homework did not reflect the  stuff learned in class and was extremely hard to understand.
